Richard Paul (actor) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Richard_Paul_(actor) 0 Richard Paul (June 6, 1940 – December 25, 1998) was an American actor who was born in Los Angeles, California. He was able to imitate most American and many foreign dialects. He had a tenor voice and trained with Lee Sweetland.
